{"tid":2404602,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"因為啊哥令我自卑","createTime":"2021-02-11T20:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T11:52:32.000Z","uid":168762,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b2276e7cafdc634bbcd7a284550fecd321d1d3a3","tid":2404602,"uid":168762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T20:17:54.000Z","msg":"我啊哥大我6 7年 係幾靚仔嗰啲呢 <br />\n由細到大佢都令我好自卑 因為我所有野都輸比佢 捉棋 打機 智識 每樣野都輸 久而久之 越嚟越自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一直覺得自己蠢 但突然發覺其實從來都係得我啊哥會話我話我蠢 諗吓諗吓 佢大我6 7 年 跟本我好多野輸比佢係好正路 跟本就唔係我廢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有一直覺得自己樣衰 因為佢成日話我樣衰 諗番轉頭 根本由細到大 係確實無人讚我靚仔 但都無人話我樣衰 柒之類 嘅野 但我就因為佢自卑咗十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人都係因為屋企人令自己自卑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9605bbb65c8a3020ee68a318d2f2e5fd34b33e","tid":2404602,"uid":118551,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T20:40:01.000Z","msg":"身高呢 邊個高啲<br />\n樣唔使太介意 現今冇人睇 身高&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;樣"},{"pid":"ede337e7bc1e696c20e9c58729aa895dc561a870","tid":2404602,"uid":179967,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T20:41:18.000Z","msg":"見到知識兩隻字你都打得錯抵你咁撚蠢"},{"pid":"f65fbe39a1b81a81c394af4104cb7d59d830d271","tid":2404602,"uid":168762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de9605bbb65c8a3020ee68a318d2f2e5fd34b33e","tid":2404602,"uid":118551,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T20:40:01.000Z","msg":"身高呢 邊個高啲<br />\n樣唔使太介意 現今冇人睇 身高&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T20:44:04.000Z","msg":"我地兩個都高大 180左右 我可能高些少<br />\n其實我都唔想介意 畢竟冇得改變 但佢由我細個開始就間中話我 樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到細個好自卑"},{"pid":"2ba6d145404e39f27ba52dc08baada3e90bffe1c","tid":2404602,"uid":389177,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T20:44:18.000Z","m